    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Octopress博客配置笔记:1]]></title>
    <link href="http://xiexiaoqi.github.io/blog/2013/10/21/octopressbo-ke-pei-zhi-bi-ji-1/"/>
    <updated>2013-10-21T17:26:00+08:00</updated>
